        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Currently, Zend_View_Helper_Translate does not escape data by itself, which means that you have to wrap its output in $this->escape() in the view, which is annoying and clutters up the view. The attached simple patch provides a convenient method to enable automatic escaping of the translated data. It is off by default for backward compatibility."
        },
